						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up near the Chennakēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1671, Prajōtpatti, Kārtika śu. 11 Wednesday.</hi> Irregular. The Cyclic and Śaka years do not tally.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record a gift of land to the god Chennakēśava at Chukalūru by Majalā of Kāśyapa <hi rend="italic">gōtra.</hi> Other details are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
